(a) that if any person’s inner self (nafs’e ammarah) is out of control and if he wants to control it, should keep his hand on chest while sleeping at night and recite YAA MUMEE-TO  100 times inshallah his purpose will be solved.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh jis shakhs ka nafs’e ammaarah us par ghaalib aa chuka ho to agar woh nafs ko apna mutee (farma bardaar) banaana chahe to us ko chahiye keh woh raat ko sotey waqt apne seeneh (chest) par haath rakh kar 100 martaba YAA MUMEE-TO ka vird karte karte so jaaye to bohot jald apne maqsad mein kaamyaab ho jaayega.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ جس شخص کا نفس امارہ اس پر غالب آچکا ہو تو اگر وہ نفس کو اپنا مطیع بنانا چاہئے تو اس کو چاہئے کہ وہ رات کو سوتے وقت اپنے سینے پر ہاتھ رکھ کر 100 مرتبہ ’’یَا مُمِیْتُ‘‘ کا ورد کرے اور ورد کرتے کرتے سوجائے تو بہت جلد اپنے مقصود میں کامیاب ہوجائے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "Arabi